#: src/Domain/Policy/AIDisclosureGenerator.php:173
msgid "We use artificial intelligence (AI) and machine learning (ML) systems to improve our services, personalize user experience, and optimize operations. This section describes how we use these technologies and your rights regarding automated data processing."
