#: src/Domain/Policy/AIDisclosureGenerator.php:180
#: src/Domain/Policy/AIDisclosureGenerator.php:227
msgid "You have the right to: (1) obtain information about the logic used in automated decision-making processes; (2) express your point of view and contest automated decisions; (3) request human intervention in automated decisions; (4) object to processing based on profiling for direct marketing purposes; (5) withdraw consent to AI-based processing when applicable."
